{
  "stem": "5371.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But being in Birkenau, I've seen so many atrocities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The women, you know, young women, walking around, half dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them were like half dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How they could walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And once the took him on the [? revere ?], which is called-- the hospital calls [? revere ?] in German.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were put to death by injection.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or, if there was enough, they took them to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, my brother, my oldest brother-- which had an accident on his-- on his place of work, where he worked-- I was told it by somebody, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went to the hospital, and they injected him with a deadly injection.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And how he was-- that's how he died in camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I had more opportunities to see more than any other-- well, there were some, you know, which had similar work of mine, but very few.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, like I said, I walked every camp, sometimes three or four times, to different camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I've seen so many terrible things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I looked at the women, you know, they were like skeletons, you know, walking around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Live skeletons.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CRYING] And then in that gypsy camp, you know, we already heard, you know, that they going to be destroyed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I didn't have the heart to tell them this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They thought that they were going to live here until the war ends, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the Germans were going to-- that's what they were told.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're going to set them up in certain areas, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're going to put them to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they didn't do any work at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, I've seen so many beautiful faces.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Young girls, so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
